node.text: ALRIGHT FOLKS, you may have seen me talking about my 75 challenge that I’ve been doing to gain some healthier habits. Super excited to team up with @profile_sanford on this and you can do the 75 Soft Challenge with me using Profile’s nutrition program and health coaching for just $75 👏🏼 Only a few more days to snag this offer - ends 8/31! Gonna put the link in my bio under the profile tab or use code: Chelsea75

node.text:
Im so in love with the newest @aubree.says product, our Woven Table Runner!! 

A runner is an easy and fashionable way to give your dining room those “adulting” vibes ❤️ Use it to frame your centerpiece, plants, or anything that you love in your gathering place. I can’t wait to see how you style your table with this beautiful piece! Head to @aubree.says to grab yours now 🤩
